<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f8fafc; }
        
        /* Container */
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        
        /* Header - green/success theme */
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .header p { opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        
        /* Main content */
        .main-content { margin: 30px 0; }
        .greeting { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #2d3748; }
        
        /* Summary stats - enhanced for weekly */
        .summary-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin: 30px 0; }
        .stat-card { background: #f7fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .stat-number { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #48bb78; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: #4a5568; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; }
        
        /* Performance highlights */
        .highlights { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fff4 0%, #c6f6d5 100%); border: 1px solid #9ae6b4; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center; }
        .highlights h3 { color: #276749; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .highlights p { color: #2f855a; font-size: 16px; }
        
        /* Section */
        .section { margin: 30px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; }
        
        /* Task list - enhanced for weekly */
        .task-list { margin: 15px 0; }
        .task-item { background: #f7fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; }
        .task-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .task-name { font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .task-project { font-size: 14px; color: #4a5568; }
        .task-badge { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .badge-completed { background: #c6f6d5; color: #276749; }
        .badge-new { background: #bee3f8; color: #2c5282; }
        .badge-overdue { background: #fed7d7; color: #c53030; }
        
        /* Progress bar */
        .progress-bar { margin: 20px 0; }
        .progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; }
        .progress-track { background: #e2e8f0; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
        .progress-fill { background: #48bb78; height: 100%; transition: width 0.3s; }
        
        /* Weekly insights */
        .insights { background: #f7fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .insights h4 { color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .insights ul { list-style: none; }
        .insights li { padding: 5px 0; color: #4a5568; position: relative; padding-left: 20px; }
        .insights li:before { content: "üí°"; position: absolute; left: 0; }
        
        /* Empty state */
        .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #718096; font-style: italic; }
        
        /* Action button */
        .action-section { text-align: center; margin: 35px 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #48bb78; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.3s; margin: 0 10px 10px 0; }
        .btn:hover { background: #38a169; }
        .btn-secondary { background: #4299e1; }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: #3182ce; }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer { background: #2d3748; color: #a0aec0; padding: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer a { color: #81e6d9; text-decoration: none; }
        .footer .divider { margin: 15px 0; height: 1px; background: #4a5568; }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content { padding: 20px; }
            .summary-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìà Weekly Digest</h1>
            <p>Your week in review for {{workspaceName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="main-content">
                <div class="greeting">
                    Hi {{userName}},
                </div>
                
                <p>Here's your weekly productivity summary. Let's celebrate your accomplishments and plan for the week ahead!</p>
                
                <!-- Performance Highlights -->
                <div class="highlights">
                    <h3>üéâ This Week's Highlights</h3>
                    <p>You completed <strong>{{summary.completedTasks}}</strong> tasks across <strong>{{summary.projectsActive}}</strong> active projects. Great momentum!</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Summary Stats -->
                <div class="summary-stats">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{summary.completedTasks}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Tasks Completed</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{summary.totalTasks}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Total Tasks</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{summary.projectsActive}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Active Projects</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{summary.teamMembers}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Team Members</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Progress Bar -->
                {{#if summary.totalTasks}}
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-label">
                        <span>Week Progress</span>
                        <span>{{summary.completedTasks}}/{{summary.totalTasks}} tasks</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="progress-track">
                        <div class="progress-fill" style="width: {{math summary.completedTasks '/' summary.totalTasks '*' 100}}%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <!-- Completed Tasks Section -->
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section-title">‚úÖ Major Accomplishments</div>
                    {{#if tasksCompleted.length}}
                        <div class="task-list">
                            {{#each tasksCompleted}}
                            <div class="task-item">
                                <div class="task-badge badge-completed">Completed</div>
                                <div class="task-name">{{name}}</div>
                                <div class="task-project">{{project_name}}</div>
                            </div>
                            {{/each}}
                        </div>
                    {{else}}
                        <div class="empty-state">Focus on completing some tasks this coming week!</div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <!-- New Assignments Section -->
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section-title">üìã New This Week</div>
                    {{#if tasksAssigned.length}}
                        <div class="task-list">
                            {{#each tasksAssigned}}
                            <div class="task-item">
                                <div class="task-badge badge-new">New</div>
                                <div class="task-name">{{name}}</div>
                                <div class="task-project">{{project_name}}</div>
                            </div>
                            {{/each}}
                        </div>
                    {{else}}
                        <div class="empty-state">No new assignments this week. Great time to focus!</div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <!-- Upcoming Deadlines Section -->
                {{#if upcomingDeadlines.length}}
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section-title">‚è∞ Week Ahead Priorities</div>
                    <div class="task-list">
                        {{#each upcomingDeadlines}}
                        <div class="task-item">
                            <div class="task-badge badge-overdue">Priority</div>
                            <div class="task-name">{{name}}</div>
                            <div class="task-project">{{project_name}} ‚Ä¢ Due soon</div>
                        </div>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <!-- Weekly Insights -->
                <div class="insights">
                    <h4>üìä Weekly Insights</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your most productive day was typically mid-week</li>
                        <li>Task completion rate: {{math summary.completedTasks '/' summary.totalTasks '*' 100 'round'}}%</li>
                        <li>Average time per task: 2.5 hours</li>
                        <li>Most active project: {{#if projectUpdates.0}}{{projectUpdates.0.project.name}}{{else}}Keep building momentum!{{/if}}</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Action Buttons -->
                <div class="action-section">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="{{reportsUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">See Detailed Reports</a>
                </div>
                
                <p>üöÄ <strong>Ready for next week?</strong> Use the insights above to plan your priorities and maintain your productivity momentum. You're doing great!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent from <strong>ProjectHub-MCP</strong></p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p>
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe from weekly digest</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>